ing rocumentaries in film, television and on the internet, the book explores the form’s rich history from the 1950s to the present day – and beyond.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aDocumentary filmsxHistory and criticism. 0aDocumentary films-History and criticism. 0aDocumentary films. 0aDocumentary television programsxHistory and criticism. 0aRock concert filmsxHistory and criticism. 0aRock music on television. 0aRock musicians in motion pictures. 4aFilm, Media & Cultural Studies. 7aMUSIC / Genres & Styles / Rock.2bisacsh1 aBaker, Michael Brendan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBell, Celine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBertrand, Karine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCampo, Javier, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChalfant, Eric, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCrowder-Taraborrelli, Tomás, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEckenroth, Lindsey, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFillion, Fillion, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFürnkranz, Magdalena, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrønstad, Asbjørn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aIversen, Gunnar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJordan, Randolph, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKibbins, Gary, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKinik, Anthony, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLobalzo Wright, Julie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb